Kinase Assay: CDK1/CycB (200 ng/measuring point) was incubated for 10 min at 22 C. in the presence of different concentrations of test substances (0 and within the range 0.001-10 uM) in assay buffer [50 mM Tris/HCl pH 8.0; 10 mM MgCl2; 0.1 mM Na ortho-vanadate; 1.0 mM dithiothreitol; 0.5 uM adenosine trisphosphate (ATP); 10 ug/measuring point histone IIIS; 0.2 uCi/measuring point 33P-gamma ATP; 0.05% NP40; 1.25% dimethyl sulphoxide]. The reaction was stopped by adding EDTA solution (250 mM; pH 8.0; 15 ul/measuring point).From each reaction mixture

The reaction was stopped by adding EDTA solution (250 mM; pH 8.0; 15 ul/measuring point).From each reaction mixture
